+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

[Description]
This file defines tab specific style classes.

[Index]
  (1) Variables
  (2) Core
  (3) Bar
    (3.0) Background
    (3.1) Title
    (3.2) Icon
    (3.3) Sizing
    (3.4) Modified
    (3.5) Dragging
    (3.6) Placeholder
  (4) Active Pane Marker

[Copyright]
